data.name: InfoBox.Text
data.value: Please note, results may vary depending on the system. How to use the program: Step 1: Make sure War Thunder + the Launcher are closed, if they are open, close them now and relaunch this program. Step 2: Launch War Thunder’s Launcher Step 3: Wait for the Text to verify the launcher is running Step 4: Click the Gear cog next to the text watch dog, enter a reasonable number. Step 5: You are all set, click Launch on your Launcher and the game should boost automatically. -------------------------------------- Optional Stuff: If you do not tab out of the game, and always stay in game, click Extra Boost, and read the prompt, this will give you a little bit more fps, like the program states, squeeze as much FPS as possible If you Tab out, and want to do normal stuff on your PC, click Remove Boost, and most applications will return to normal, please note you will still have war thunder in boosted mode. Click on Boost again before you tab back in. If you find that boost impacts your gameplay, click restore, finish your gameplay and restart your game without the booster program.
